title: Supreme Models
overview: Supreme Models is a documentary focusing on the Black models shattering the barriers in the modeling industry and how they've revolutionized the standards of fashion and beauty. And weighing in on the importance of Black models and their impact on fashion and society are the world's most influential editors, famous fashion designers, and the supermodels themselves. Featuring Iman, Karen Alexander, Joan Smalls, Olivier Rousteing, Anna Wintour and SO many more.
